Step 1 : Add banner HTML to your homepage template
<div class="welcome-banner">
    <p>Welcome to Our Restaurant</p>
</div>

Step 2 : Style the banner
.welcome-banner {
    background-color: #ff6347;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px 0;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.welcome-banner p {
    margin: 0;
}

Step 3 : Link CSS in base template
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{% static 'css/style.css' %}">


Step 4 : Tailwind CSS
<div class="bg-red-500 text-white py-4 text-center text-lg font-bold tracking-wide">
    Welcome to Our Restaurant !
</div>


****Result****
> A colored banner at the top of your homepage with a bold welcome message.
> Uses either plain CSS or TailwindCSS, depending on your setup.

